description:
"Touhou Youyoumu Arrangements Pack Vol.2" is a collection of popular arrangement tracks from the rhythm game including "What about progress?", "Necrofantasia ～Arr.Demetori" and more.
Enjoy all the lovely songs as good as vol.1!

A new artist has been added to this set: 
FULING CAT MARK!

This pack contains the following: 

■6 Songs
　・What about progress? / sumijun(Halozy) feat. nanahira(Confetto)
　・MARIONETTE METROPOLIS / FULING CAT MARK
　・Sissou Ensemble / beatMARIO(COOL&CREATE)
　・Genuineness Almeria / Shinra-Bansho
　・Fallen Cherry Blossom / Yuuhei Satellite
　・Necrofantasia ～Arr.Demetori / Demetori

■6 Challenge Stages
　・Lv.5 What's the progress now?! (What about progress?)
　・Lv.6 I'm not a waitress! (MARIONETTE METROPOLIS)
　・Lv.7 The fastest of all!(Sissou Ensemble)
　・Lv.8 Almeria (Genuineness Almeria)
　・Lv.9 Kanzashi (Fallen Cherry Blossom)
　・Lv.10 The doorkeeper proxy (Necrofantasia ～Arr.Demetori)

* Internet connection required for purchase. 
* Game must be restarted after songs are purchased in order to use them.
name: Touhou Youyoumu Arrangements Pack Vol.2
